pageContext.claim: “New Mexico has a tremendous problem with people pouring across New Mexico, and I'm hearing because of this, New Mexico is actually in play for me and for the Republicans because of what’s happening.”
pageContext.analysis: There have been an increase in border crossings in New Mexico, but that doesn't mean the state is “in play” for Trump. The Albuquerque Journal reported only 38 percent of New Mexico voters approved of “the job Trump was doing as president.”
